{"tid":1634913,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣人作咗首新詩比我哋","createTime":"2019-10-07T10:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T16:45:30.000Z","uid":128804,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e8010e35f49ee03543766cb285b02dfa4eca10","tid":1634913,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:43:52.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得10.1 依張相?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBxrTgk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBxrTgk.jpg&h=cafe4e76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺台灣ptt,依張圖引發咗極大迴響同共鳴<br />\n同時,有一首新詩都喺ptt度流傳<br />\n而作者相信係台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n《我的遺書在口袋裡了》  作者:coco1104520 (榛)<br />\n<br />\n親愛的<br />\n我的遺書在口袋裏了<br />\n如果我倒下<br />\n頭盔上有標註血型<br />\n只對暴政反感<br />\n對藥物沒有過敏<br />\n<br />\n親愛的<br />\n我的遺書在口袋裏了<br />\n如果心被射穿<br />\n如果被毆到牙落<br />\n請別救我                                                                        <br />\n去讀這片土地上的血汗<br />\n我和山川融為一體<br />\n<br />\n親愛的                                                                          <br />\n我的遺書在口袋裏了<br />\n如果你翻開                                                                      <br />\n上頭寫滿的是對不起<br />\n對不起，我不是個好後生<br />\n也可能不是個好情人<br />\n這些日子讓你們受累<br />\n<br />\n提醒爸爸白天多運動<br />\n媽媽晚上少喝點<br />\n上週給奶奶買的禮物在床下<br />\n我離開後，請妹妹替我找出來<br />\n好嗎？  <br />\n<br />\n原諒我，理解我<br />\n為我感覺光榮<br />\n好嗎？<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n                                                                                <br />\n我們手裡沒有籌碼<br />\n只好拿自己未來下注<br />\n單數是卑躬屈膝<br />\n雙數是接受籠絡<br />\n於是硬在世間闢出一個零             <br />\n希望一切回到原點，回到當年<br />\n沒有槍桿指向咽喉<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n                                                                                <br />\n親愛的<br />\n我的遺書在口袋裏了<br />\n無路可退的人<br />\n沒辦法保證是否還有明天<br />\n但能驕傲地說<br />\n一路上我清楚，即使畏虎<br />\n也要面對血盆大口<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n                                                                                <br />\n親愛的我城<br />\n願榮光終歸於你<br />\n我的遺書在口袋裏了<br />\n如果來生，如果有來生<br />\n再讓我看你一眼</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想講少少嘢<br />\n我覺得香港而家係少咗一啲情感上嘅動力<br />\n<br />\n個人認為依一首詩, 同埋喺「明泰弟弟的醫院日記」fb page 嗰個「重光之後,你想做咩工作?」嘅post一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我相信如果佢哋可以喺連儂牆上出現,一定可以幫大家延續抗爭落去嘅動力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我嘅出文宣能力係有限公司<br />\n但我唔希望假手於人,直接講「文宣組做嘢」<br />\n今晚開始, 我會盡我所能去畫文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然都希望有人可以一齊畫~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港   時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n[新聞] 《我的遺書在口袋裡了》瘋傳 港人大雨中持續抗議<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1570413241.A.5A1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1570413241.A.5A1.html&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=dcf94245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1570413241.A.5A1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n[創作] 我的遺書在口袋裏了<br />\ncoco1104520 (榛)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/poem/M.1569943178.A.66C.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fpoem%2FM.1569943178.A.66C.html&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=347a75e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/poem/M.1569943178.A.66C.html</a>"},{"pid":"fa74f2b3e99d0e005bfc178e3e39d6a2a7a21cff","tid":1634913,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:50:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30a3ebc9938f2fe2ed6d65b7a53292edb5a16e5f","tid":1634913,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9969d09e2c1a38a2b58c539bda9d6fce756259","tid":1634913,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac87f0a4b6b33966c632ef1662db76ffed6ba147","tid":1634913,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ef858b02b7572acc562cbeaa416b4b795a26869","tid":1634913,"uid":6882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:12:44.000Z","msg":"感人 推"},{"pid":"4af53332a9da9fecd7f961791efa967d5ecf18f0","tid":1634913,"uid":58896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:13:23.000Z","msg":"睇到張原圖已經想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇埋呢首詩發覺兩頰已經涼浸浸<br />\n原來兩行淚已經流下來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3b3c2b0b83ce17c4325bab3483f867b6a457b8","tid":1634913,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"諗起自己寫個遺書個陣既心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喊左"},{"pid":"48c0f78bc2d9bcbe10bcd35fac11ef9d7f38f98a","tid":1634913,"uid":173552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0c25ea4d625b31f35a4abfe242ef43e0211ba2","tid":1634913,"uid":128804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:18:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c9f4724666888ee189365a41337364e4e57a