書在口袋裏了<br />\n無路可退的人<br />\n沒辦法保證是否還有明天<br />\n但能驕傲地說<br />\n一路上我清楚，即使畏虎<br />\n也要面對血盆大口<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n                                                                                <br />\n親愛的我城<br />\n願榮光終歸於你<br />\n我的遺書在口袋裏了<br />\n如果來生，如果有來生<br />\n再讓我看你一眼</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想講少少嘢<br />\n我覺得香港而家係少咗一啲情感上嘅動力<br />\n<br />\n個人認為依一首詩, 同埋喺「明泰弟弟的醫院日記」fb page 嗰個「重光之後,你想做咩工作?」嘅post一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我相信如果佢哋可以喺連儂牆上出現,一定可以幫大家延續抗爭落去嘅動力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我嘅出文宣能力係有限公司<br />\n但我唔希望假手於人,直接講「文宣組做嘢」<br />\n今晚開始, 我會盡我所能去畫文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然都希望有人可以一齊畫~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港   時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n[新聞] 《我的遺書在口袋裡了》瘋傳 港人大雨中持續抗議<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1570413241.A.5A1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1570413241.A.5A1.html&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=dcf94245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1570413241.A.5A1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n[創作] 我的遺書在口袋裏了<br />\ncoco1104520 (榛)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/poem/M.1569943178.A.66C.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fpoem%2FM.1569943178.A.66C.html&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=347a75e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/poem/M.1569943178.A.66C.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:38:12.000Z","msg":"係咪抄血染的風采架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca5b25c0f6e9248f98c8200c8829eecdc7fd490","tid":1634913,"uid":205736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:45:30.000Z","msg